"<!-- NAV: same as homepage SiteHeader, see raw-nav.json --><div class=\"fixed top-[88px] left-0 right-0 z-30 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out opacity-100 transform translate-y-0\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 flex justify-between items-center\"><button class=\"flex items-center space-x-1 bg-white/90 dark:bg-gray-800/90 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-gray-800\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun w-4 h-4 transition-colors text-orange-600\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><div class=\"relative w-6 h-3 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-600 rounded-full transition-colors\"><div class=\"absolute top-0.5 w-2 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-600 rounded-full shadow-sm transition-transform duration-200 translate-x-0.5\"></div></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon w-4 h-4 transition-colors text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400\"><path d=\"M12 3a6 6 0 0 0 9 9 9 9 0 1 1-9-9Z\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"flex items-center space-x-1 bg-white/90 dark:bg-gray-800/90 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-gray-800\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium transition-colors text-orange-600\">EN</span><div class=\"relative w-6 h-3 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-600 rounded-full transition-colors\"><div class=\"absolute top-0.5 w-2 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-600 rounded-full shadow-sm transition-transform duration-200 translate-x-0.5\"></div></div><span class=\"text-xs font-medium transition-colors text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400\">ES</span></button></div></div><div class=\"pt-[calc(64px+2rem)] min-h-screen\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"flex flex-col mb-16\"><span class=\"relative flex shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-full w-24 h-24 border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-600 shadow-lg mb-6\"><img class=\"aspect-square h-full w-full\" alt=\"Caleb Ixca\" src=\"/lovable-uploads/8bce85f6-2015-40ce-849b-efeb500ddf88.png\"></span><div class=\"space-y-6 text-base lg:text-lg text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-figtree leading-relaxed font-bold text-left\"><p>👋🏾 Hola, I'm Caleb Ixca. AI-powered designer, founder, and artist. I've been building since I was 14, from teaching kids art to showing work in galleries. That creative spark now powers my work leading product and experience at <span class=\"underline font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400\">Persona X</span>, an AI platform helping teams understand their customers. Along the way, I've designed at <span class=\"underline font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400\">Affirm</span>, <span class=\"underline font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400\">Streetcode</span>, and <span class=\"underline font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400\">Sumo Logic</span>, and taught UX/UI to students entering tech.</p><p>I've been lucky to learn from incredible mentors, and I'm passionate about paying it forward, whether through mentorship, collaboration, or honest conversation. Let's connect and make it personal.</p></div></div><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-lexend\">Experience</h2><div class=\"space-y-12\"><div class=\"flex gap-8\"><div class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium min-w-[80px] font-figtree\">2023</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-lexend\">Co-Founder, Head of Product &amp; Experience at Persona X</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-figtree\">2 years • Present</p></div><p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-figtree\">Co-founded an AI Customer Intelligence platform that helps product teams turn customer data into actionable insights. Led product strategy, design, and go-to-market execution from concept to MVP launch.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8\"><div class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium min-w-[80px] font-figtree\">2022</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-lexend\">Designer at Affirm</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-figtree\">8 months</p></div><p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-figtree\">Designed internal tools for Capital Markets, including a self-service deal management system and a real-time risk dashboard. Focused on clarity, scalability, and auditability.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8\"><div class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium min-w-[80px] font-figtree\">2021</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-lexend\">UX/ UI Intern at Ring Central</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-figtree\">6 months</p></div><p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-figtree\">Collaborated on new features for the collaboration suite, prototyping and testing workflows in short, research-driven sprints.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8\"><div class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium min-w-[80px] font-figtree\">2019-2021</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-lexend\">UX/UI teacher (Educator), Digital Experience (Internal) at Streetcode</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-figtree\">2 years</p></div><p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-figtree\">Taught UX/UI to underrepresented students and led a website redesign for the nonprofit to improve usability and engagement.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8\"><div class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium min-w-[80px] font-figtree\">2019</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-lexend\">Designer at Remediant</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-figtree\">7 months</p></div><p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-figtree\">Designed the MVP and implemented a scalable design system for a cybersecurity startup focused on privileged access management.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8\"><div class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium min-w-[80px] font-figtree\">2018</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-lexend\">In-house designer, Training and Documentation team at Sumo Logic</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-figtree\">1 year • 10 months</p></div><p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-figtree\">Redesigned the documentation site and certification program, and prototyped a mobile dashboard for real-time analytics during a company hackathon.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div>"